  • Emollients — apply liberally + frequently (within 3 min after bath); thick creams/ointments preferred over lotions;
  • Bathing: daily warm short, mild non-soap cleanser, moisturize immediately; bleach baths for recurrent infections (¼ cup bleach in tub);
