(8) Relapse common — multiple attempts typical; don't discourage;

(9) Special populations: pregnant (behavioral first; NRT if needed; varenicline + bupropion limited data), cardiovascular (varenicline + NRT safe per EAGLES + meta-analyses), mental health (varenicline + bupropion safety reaffirmed EAGLES), opioid/methadone, adolescents (limited pharm — behavioral + NRT cautious);

