  • Pre-pregnancy optimize TSH < 2.5;
  • During pregnancy ↑ dose ~ 30% (more thyroid demand);
  • Trimester-specific TSH ranges;

(6) Older adults: less aggressive — TSH 4-6 acceptable; avoid overtreatment (AFib, osteoporosis, mortality);

