  • TURP (transurethral resection) — gold standard;
  • HoLEP (Holmium laser enucleation), GreenLight laser — alternatives;
  • Minimally invasive: UroLift (prostatic urethral lift), Rezum (water vapor), iTind, Aquablation, prostatic artery embolization;
  • Open / robotic simple prostatectomy for very large;

(6) Complications watch: urinary retention, recurrent UTI, hematuria, bladder stones, hydronephrosis, AKI;

(7) Multidisciplinary: PCP + urology referral for refractory / complications / surgical candidate
