  • Cardiac (ECG — QTc, arrhythmia);
  • Electrolytes (hypokalemia from purging), glucose, BUN, Cr, Mg, phos;
  • CBC;
  • LFT;
  • TSH, FSH/LH/estradiol;
  • DXA bone density (osteoporosis common);
  • Dental (purging erosion);
  • EKG;

(4) Screening tools: SCOFF questionnaire; EAT-26; comprehensive interview;

