  • Tocilizumab (IL-6 inhibitor) — FDA approved 2017 — steroid-sparing, reduce flare, dual therapy; can shorten/reduce steroid;
  • Methotrexate — alternative steroid-sparing;
  • Prednisone tapered to lowest effective;

(6) Treatment PMR:
  • Low-dose prednisone 15-20 mg/d → response rapid (often dramatic) → taper slowly over 1-2 yr;
  • Methotrexate steroid-sparing for relapse;
  • Tocilizumab in selected (especially GCA + PMR);

