  • MSM/TGW (multiple/anonymous partners, condomless, recent STI, sex while substance use);
  • Heterosexual (partner HIV+ not virally suppressed, multiple partners, condomless, recent STI, sex worker);
  • PWID (people who inject drugs — sharing, partners HIV+);
  • Anyone who requests;

