  • STI screening (syphilis, chlamydia, gonorrhea — multi-site MSM);
  • Pregnancy test if applicable (PrEP safe in pregnancy);
  • Renal function (eGFR ≥ 60 for Truvada; ≥ 30 for Descovy);
  • Bone density if osteoporosis risk;

