  • Long-acting injectable:
  • Cabotegravir (Apretude) — FDA-approved 2021 — IM injection q 2 mo (after 1 mo loading); high efficacy + adherence; cost + access barriers;
  • Future: lenacapavir SC q 6 mo (PURPOSE-1 + 2 trials 2024);

