  • LEEP (loop electrosurgical excision procedure) — most common, outpatient, local anesthesia;
  • Cold knife conization — alternative;
  • Ablative (cryotherapy, laser, thermal) for selected CIN2 — must rule out invasion first;
  • For young + want fertility — consider observation CIN2 (regression possible);

