  • ASC-US: HPV reflex; if positive → colposcopy or repeat 1 yr based on risk;
  • LSIL: colposcopy;
  • HSIL or ASC-H: colposcopy + biopsy;
  • AGC (atypical glandular): colposcopy + endocervical sampling + endometrial sampling if ≥ 35 or abnormal bleeding;

