(7) Food insecurity screening + intervention: critical SDOH;

(8) Food + medication interactions: warfarin + vit K, MAOI + tyramine, grapefruit + meds;

(9) Cultural considerations + personalization;

(10) Nutrition counseling: brief in primary care; refer dietitian / RDN for comprehensive; Medicare benefit DM, CKD;

(11) Lifestyle medicine integration;

(12) Multidisciplinary: PCP + RDN/dietitian + diabetes educator + behavioral health + community programs + SDOH resources
