Sleep: 7-9 h adult; sleep hygiene foundation. Major disorders — insomnia (CBT-I), OSA (CPAP), RLS (iron + gabapentinoid), narcolepsy (sleep med referral), parasomnias. Pediatric considerations. Pregnancy + mental health bidirectional. Drowsy driving + tech. Multidisciplinary.

